    <bodyTop>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead-big"><strong>Why QMU?</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span class="lead-big"><strong>Our staff have real world experience of working in the events sector.</strong></span></li>
<li><span class="lead-big"><strong>All our courses blend theory with practice to ensure you are learning skills you can put to use in your work.</strong></span></li>
<li><span class="lead-big"><strong>We have been teaching courses in events management for many years.</strong></span></li>
</ul>]]></Value>
