    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><strong>This course will help you to develop knowledge and understanding about the practical implementation of both sustainable development policies and health and safety principles for those working in the event industries. The first half of the course focuses on the topic of sustainable event management while the second half focuses on managing health and safety at events.</strong></p>]]></Value>
